(3339, 1, '2015-12-04 05:45:59', '2015-12-04 05:45:59', '<p>\r\nWe have more than thirty years experience in making and supplying laboratory furniture especially for universities. Tables, cupboards, stools and other timber furniture are produced on customer request. Prices of these items vary with the customers requirements and not included to standard product price list.\r\n</p>', 'Laboratory Furniture', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'laboratory-furniture', '', '', '2015-12-14 03:55:17', '2015-12-14 03:55:17', '', 0, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/?post_type=product&#038;p=3339', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(3340, 1, '2015-12-04 05:46:23', '2015-12-04 05:46:23', '<p>\r\nProducts, tools and equipments for roads maintenance are manufactured on customer request. Tar Boiler of 60 & 120 Gallon, Tar Patching sets, Wheel Barrows, Gulley Grating Frame & Cover of standard sizes, Cast iron Stampers 7.5 kg,    Manhole Frame & Covers rectangular and circular standard sizes are made out of mild steel sheets, rods, angles, Galvanized Iron pipe, and cast iron using casting, welding, and metal fabrication processes.\r\n</p>', 'Road Maintenance Equipment', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'road-maintenance-equipment', '', '', '2015-12-04 10:44:11', '2015-12-04 10:44:11', '', 0, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/?post_type=product&#038;p=3340', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(3341, 1, '2015-12-04 05:46:39', '2015-12-04 05:46:39', '<p>\r\nHousehold and gardening tools are produced in light fabrication workshop on customer requests. Medium carbon steel and mild steel are used as  materials  in making these products. The following products are included in the standard product price lists.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWooden furniture such as tables, beds, cupboards, racks, stools, benches etc are manufactured on customer requests. Prices of these items are not included in the standards product price list. Timber will be selected as requested by customers and classifications of timber for these products are in accordance with the State Timber Corporation classification.Powder coating of steel furniture is one of the new value added service for customers.\r\n</p>', 'Household Tools & Furniture', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'household-tools-furniture', '', '', '2015-12-04 10:54:35', '2015-12-04 10:54:35', '', 0, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/?post_type=product&#038;p=3341', 0, 'product', '', 0),
