(3379, 1, '2015-12-04 06:34:37', '2015-12-04 06:34:37', '<p>\r\nThe following standard products are manufactured on customer requests in Machining and Millwright and Light Engineering workshop. The prices are  included in the standard price lists.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	\r\n<blockquote><li>Punchers</li>\r\n	<li>Call Bell</li>\r\n	<li>Bodkin Binder</li>\r\n	<li>Embossing Machines (Cast iron)</li></blockquote>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n', 'Office Equipment', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'office-equipment', '', '', '2015-12-04 10:36:38', '2015-12-04 10:36:38', '', 0, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/?post_type=product&#038;p=3379', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(3381, 1, '2015-12-04 06:37:08', '2015-12-04 06:37:08', '<p>\r\nThe following wooden office furniture is manufactured in the carpentry workshop on customer requests. The steel furniture are manufactured in either Light Fabrication workshop or in Machining and Millwright. The prices are not included in the standard item price lists. Steel products can be powder coated.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<blockquote><li>Executive Table & Ordinary Table (Wooden)</li>\r\n	<li>Chairs (Wooden or Steel)</li>\r\n	<li>Racks (wooden or Steel)</li>\r\n	<li>Computer Table ( MDF)</li></blockquote>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'Office Furniture', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'office-furniture', '', '', '2015-12-14 03:55:24', '2015-12-14 03:55:24', '', 0, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/?post_type=product&#038;p=3381', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(3382, 1, '2015-12-04 07:42:41', '2015-12-04 07:42:41', '<p>\nHealth sector has been our major customer more than three decades and originally provided mostly steel furniture with painted finish for most of the hospitals.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nThere are about 30 odd steel items in the standard product list, Variety of Beds, trolleys, cupboards, wheel chairs, Baby cots, and various types of Stands etc.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nSome products are made out of Stainless steel with better finish.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nElectroplating techniques has also been used for better finish of some products for several decades.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nPowder coating of hospital furniture has been introduced since last year for increasing demand for better surface finish and durability from health sector.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nProduct development is always encouraged and our engineers are ready for meeting customer needs in the health Sector giving consultancy services for preparation of specifications and product development to cater local needs and requirement of general public.\n</p>', 'Hospital Furniture', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3337-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-04 07:42:41', '2015-12-04 07:42:41', '', 3337, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/3337-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
