actory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/blue-bullet.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3624" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/blue-bullet.jpg" alt="blue-bullet" width="8" height="7" /></a>  Sticker Cutting\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/blue-bullet.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3624" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/blue-bullet.jpg" alt="blue-bullet" width="8" height="7" /></a>  Digital Printing</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"><a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="12" height="13" /></a>  Lock repairs\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="12" height="13" /></a>  Engraving of Engine &amp; Chassis Numbers\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="12" height="13" /></a>  Saw Doctoring\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="12" height="13" /></a>  Fire Bucket (GI Sheet 24 gauge) 11" diameter\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="12" height="13" /></a>  Dustbin GI 