(3603, 1, '2015-12-17 05:40:22', '2015-12-17 05:40:22', 'Core work area of the Government Factory in the heavy fabrication section is now being Design, Fabrication and Installation of Radial Gates, Stop Log Gates, Sluice Gates and any kind of gates for Water Management Purposes.\r\n\r\nFabrication, repairs, replacement and installation of accessories and operating mechanisms of water management gates made out of timber, cast iron, structural steel and stainless steels are major works which re<img class="size-full wp-image-3660 alignright" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/penstock-gate-repairs-services-250x250.jpg" alt="penstock-gate-repairs-services-250x250" width="250" height="187" />presented nearly seventy percent (70%) of the total work load of 2009.\r\n\r\nMetal forming, cutting, drilling, machining, Arc, Gas, Tig &amp; Mig Welding, Plasma Cutting &amp; Gas Cutting, Sand Blasting, Airless Spray Painting Work, and Galvanizing are operations involved in performing the above work and services. Our workshops are equipped with the necessary plant, machinery, and equipment to perform the above operations except galvanizing.\r\n\r\nInspection and testing of welding works is carried out by selecting an authorized Inspector from a list, recommended by the Institution of Engineers Sri Lanka.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="15" height="16" /></a>    Deduru Projects – Fabrication &amp; Installation of 8 Nos Radial Gates,cost 155.5 Mn, in year 2012\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-3631" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bullet-checkmark.png" alt="bullet-checkmark" width="15" height="16" /></a>    Rambakan Projec