ent/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Verification of usable and obsolete capital assets and condemning them, valuation and selling.\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Execution of projects, tasks, special erection work assigned by the Secretary of the Ministry, Ministry of Public administration or Presidential secretariat.\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Execution of tender awards, special work orders, undertaken by the marketing division of the Government Factory.\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Provision of safer and cleaner working environment &amp; welfare facilities to employees.</blockquote>\r\n<h5>Marketing</h5>\r\n<blockquote><a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Provision of estimates for products, works &amp; services for internal and external clients/ customers\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Selling and distribution of products and services.\r\n<a href="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3626" src="http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/tick_white.png" alt="tick_white" width="16" height="16" /></a>  Acquisition of work orders by competitive bidding.</blockquote>\r\n<h5>Human Resources Development and Management</h5>\r\n<h5>Procurement</h5>\r\n<h5>Planning and Development</h5>\r\n<h5>Financial Accounting</h5>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4>History</h4>\r\nGovernment Factory was a sub department of Public Works Department, Originally established at Pettah, on Gas Workers Street, in 1849. It was shifted to the present location at Kolonnawa in 1928, as a part or sub department of the Public Works Department to Provide the Mechanical Engineering support for the Operation of many Public institutions at that time. With the breaking up of the Public Works Department into Highways and Buildings Departments from 01/10/1969, followed by the creation of the Territorial Civil Engineering Organization in 1971, the Government Factory became a Class “A” Department with effect from 01/10/1971.\r\n\r\nOriginal role of the Government Factory was to provide Mechanical Engineering Works, Products, Equipments and allied Operations, Maintenance and repair of Plant and Machinery required for development of infrastructure, for Construction of Roads, Bridges, and Ferry Boats, Irrigation Water Management, and Building Maintenance.\r\n\r\nOnce the Government Factory became a Class “A” Department, Functions of the Factory has been operated under Advance Accounts of the General Treasury. Government Factory has been attached to the following Ministries during the last four decades, Lands and Land Development, Housing &amp; Construction, Housing &amp; Public Utilities, and Currently Construction and Engineering Services.\r\n\r\n[/one_whole]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Overview and History', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3069-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-16 10:05:57', '2015-12-16 10:05:57', '', 3069, 'http://sdu.ucsc.lk/govtfactory/3069-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
